---
// GrinduroExplainer.astro — Grinduro format explainer (CONT-06)
// Magazine editorial layout: CSS Grid full-bleed with tone image breaks
---
<section class="explainer-grid py-8 mb-8">
  <p class="text-text-muted text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4" data-reveal>Grinduro Format</p>

  <p class="explainer-drop-cap text-text-body text-sm leading-relaxed" data-reveal>
    This isn&apos;t a time trial. It&apos;s a mass-start sufferfest with structure.
  </p>

  <div class="full-bleed relative overflow-hidden my-6" style="height: 260px;" data-reveal>
    <img
      src="/tone/square-limit-mc-escher.webp"
      alt=""
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="tone-image inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
      style="opacity: 0.40; filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(2.5) brightness(0.55);"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>

  <p class="text-text-body text-sm leading-relaxed" data-reveal>
    <strong class="text-accent-white">Seven gravel sectors</strong> are timed &mdash;
    rated 1&ndash;5 stars by surface brutality, Paris-Roubaix style.
    <strong class="text-accent-green">Three KOM/QOM climbs</strong> are timed separately &mdash;
    fastest up takes the segment.
  </p>

  <blockquote class="pull-quote" data-reveal>
    Race the sectors. Suffer together.
  </blockquote>

  <div class="full-bleed relative overflow-hidden my-6" style="height: 260px;" data-reveal>
    <img
      src="/tone/pan-escher-nat-world.webp"
      alt=""
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="tone-image inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
      style="opacity: 0.35; filter: grayscale(100%) sepia(80%) hue-rotate(60deg) saturate(4) contrast(1.4) brightness(0.7);"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>

  <p class="text-text-body text-sm leading-relaxed" data-reveal>
    Everything between? Challenging, remote, and utterly untimed.
    Ride your own ride. Race the sectors. Suffer together.
  </p>
</section>
